1770 GOTO 1430
1780 REM
1790 REM GRAFIEK TEKENEN **************
1800 CN=0:GOSUB 600
1810 HO=0:VE=0:SR$=PL$
1820 GOSUB 650
1830 SR$=""
1840 FOR X=1 TO LEN(PL$)
1850 SR$=SR$+"-"
1860 NEXT X
