1880 REM
1890 HO=.2:VE=.2:GOSUB 620
1900 VE=.8:GOSUB 630
1910 HO=.8:GOSUB 630
1920 VE=.2:GOSUB 630
1930 REM
1940 FOR X=0 TO 30 STEP 10
1950 HO=.13:VE=.8-X*.02
