1970 HO=.82:VE=.8-X*.02
1980 GOSUB 650:NEXT X
1990 REM
2000 FOR X=1 TO 12
2010 HO=.17+.05*X:VE=.85
2020 SR$=LEFT$(MA$(X),1)
2030 GOSUB 650
2040 NEXT X
2050 REM
