2100 GOSUB 630
2110 VE=.8:GOSUB 630
2120 NEXT X
2130 REM
2140 HO=.2:VE=.8-TE(12)/50:GOSUB 620
2150 FOR X=1 TO 12
2160 HO=.175+X*.05:VE=.8-TE(X)/50
2170 GOSUB 630
2180 NEXT X
2190 HO=.8:VE=.8-TE(1)/50:GOSUB 630
